WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.360 --> 00:00:03.300
"Hello / How Are You?"

00:00:03.380 --> 00:00:04.960
"Kizuna AI"

00:00:05.220 --> 00:00:06.460
♪ Hello! ♪
(haro)

00:00:06.460 --> 00:00:10.120
♪ I opened my window and whispered ♪
(mado o akete chiisaku tsubuyaita)

00:00:10.120 --> 00:00:11.640
♪ How are you? ♪
(hawayu)

00:00:11.640 --> 00:00:14.940
♪ Alone in my room, with no one ♪
(dare mo inai heya de hitori)

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:16.440
♪ Morning! ♪
(moonin)

00:00:16.660 --> 00:00:20.440
♪ The morning has arrived, with a heavy downpour ♪
(asa ga kita yo doshaburi no asa ga)

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:21.460
♪ Tick-tock ♪
(tikutaku)

00:00:21.700 --> 00:00:27.280
♪ Someone please rewind my spring for me ♪
(watashi no neji o dare ka maite)

00:00:48.260 --> 00:00:49.180
♪ Hello! ♪
(haro)

00:00:49.320 --> 00:00:53.000
♪ I think that kind of person appeared only in old anime ♪
(mukashi no anime ni sonna no ita kke na)

00:00:53.340 --> 00:00:54.320
♪ How are you? ♪
(hawayu)

00:00:54.580 --> 00:00:58.040
♪ I am so jealous, that someone can be loved by all ♪
(urayamashii na minna ni aisarete)

00:00:58.240 --> 00:00:59.120
♪ Sleeping... ♪
(suriipin)

00:00:59.440 --> 00:01:02.860
♪ I must stop saying silly things and start preparing ♪
(baka na koto itte naide shitaku o shinakucha)

00:01:03.300 --> 00:01:04.120
♪ Crying... ♪
(kurain)

00:01:04.500 --> 00:01:08.000
♪ In order to hide my tear marks ♪
(namida no ato o kakusu tame)

00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:11.160
♪ "Oh well, whatever" has become my favorite phrase ♪
(mou kuchiguse ni natta "maa-ikka")

00:01:11.360 --> 00:01:14.280
♪ That line from yesterday went straight over my head: ♪
(kinou no kotoba ga futo atama o yogiru)

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:18.680
♪ "I don't have any expectations of you anymore" ♪
("mou kimi ni wa zenzen kitai shite'nai kara")

00:01:19.020 --> 00:01:21.260
♪ Well, even I myself ♪
(sorya maa watashi datte)

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:23.960
♪ Won't have any expectations of myself, but still ♪
(jibun ni kitai nado shite'nai keredo)

00:01:24.340 --> 00:01:28.140
♪ What was THAT for? ♪
(are wa ittai dou iu tsumori desu ka)

00:01:29.080 --> 00:01:34.260
♪ The words that escaped from my throat ♪
(nodomoto made dekakatta kotoba)

00:01:34.480 --> 00:01:36.680
♪ Were nothing ♪
(kuchi o tsuite)

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:38.500
♪ But lies ♪
(deta no wa uso)

00:01:38.780 --> 00:01:43.720
♪ Today too, I've wasted some valuable words ♪
(kou shite kyou mo watashi wa kichou na)

00:01:43.980 --> 00:01:48.480
♪ As I continue living my life ♪
(kotoba o rouhi shite ikite yuku)

00:01:48.860 --> 00:01:51.600
♪ Why is it that you end up hiding it? ♪
(naze kakushite shimau no desu ka)

00:01:51.720 --> 00:01:53.980
♪ Is it that you're scared of being laughed at? ♪
(warawareru no ga kowai no desu ka)

00:01:54.200 --> 00:01:56.860
♪ Is it that you don't want to meet anyone? ♪
(dare ni mo aitakunai no desu ka)

00:01:56.860 --> 00:01:58.960
♪ Is that really true? ♪
(sore hontou desu ka)

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:01.900
♪ Drowning in a sea of the name "ambiguity" ♪
(aimai to iu na no umi ni oborete)

00:02:01.980 --> 00:02:03.920
♪ I'm suffering because I can no longer breathe ♪
(iki mo dekinai hodo kurushii no)

00:02:04.180 --> 00:02:06.600
♪ I now have a small urge to listen to someone's voice ♪
(sukoshi koe ga kikitaku narimashita)

00:02:06.600 --> 00:02:08.600
♪ I am so weak ♪
(hontou ni yowai na)

00:02:09.080 --> 00:02:10.500
♪ Hau~ ♪

